Description: validateHOT is a package that validates validation/ holdout tasks (HOTs) in (adaptive) Conjoint analysis as well as MaxDiff. You define the Holdout task and afterward, choose different validation metrics. validateHOT is a user-friendly tool to help you test the predictive validity of your data.
